Board of Directors: Bobby Kotick












Share:

























































Bobby Kotick
President, Chief Executive Officer
 and Director
Activision Blizzard, Inc.
 
Bobby Kotick has been a Director of The Coca-Cola Company since 2012.  Mr. Kotick is President, Chief Executive Officer and a Director of Activision Blizzard, Inc., a leading global developer and publisher of interactive entertainment, and has held these positions since 2008. Mr. Kotick served as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of the predecessor to Activision Blizzard, Inc. from 1991 to 2008. Mr. Kotick is the co-founder of the Call of Duty Endowment, a non-profit that has helped over 25,000 veterans find high-quality careers after military service.







